### ==============================
### Computer Management API Flow
### ==============================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### GET all computers
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET computers by filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers?department=IT&status=Active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### SEARCH computers
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers/search?q=PC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET stats by department
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers/stats/by-dept
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST create computer
POST {{baseUrl}}/computers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeNo": "EMP-DEMO-001",
  "email": "demo-computer@example.com",
  "phone": "0900000000",
  "userName": "Demo User",
  "position": "Engineer",
  "department": "IT",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.100",
  "macAddress": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:11",
  "computerName": "PC-DEMO-001",
  "userNamePc": "demo.user",
  "categories": "Laptop",
  "manufacturer": "Dell",
  "serviceTag": "SV-DEMO-001",
  "systemModel": "Latitude 7440",
  "cpu": "Intel Core i7",
  "ram": "16GB",
  "hdd": "",
  "ssd": "512GB",
  "vga": "Intel Iris Xe",
  "other": "",
  "status": "Active",
  "notes": "Create from reques.http"
}

### PUT update computer by id
PUT {{baseUrl}}/computers/REPLACE_COMPUTER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Under Maintenance",
  "ram": "32GB",
  "notes": "Updated from reques.http"
}

### DELETE computer by id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/computers/REPLACE_COMPUTER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### EXPORT computers to Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### EXPORT computers to Excel with filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers/export?department=IT&status=Active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### DOWNLOAD import template Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/computers/template
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### IMPORT computers from Excel
POST {{baseUrl}}/computers/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="computers-import.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./computers-import.xlsx
--WebAppBoundary--